The second [[official alternate costume|costume]] of [[indie virtual youtuber|indie VTuber]] [[Fallenshadow]].

It is a composite costume with three distinct appearances, with the core shared article of clothes being [[white pantyhose]] with [[leg ribbon]]s, as well as a frilled underskirt and [[black footwear|black]] [[boots]] for the core dress appearances. The three distinct appearances this costume can depict are:
* A [[frills|frilled]], [[purple dress|light purple dress]] with [[puffy sleeves]], and a [[purple hat|matching]] [[beret]] (post #6420040);
* A [[purple dress|dark purple]] [[pinafore dress]] over a [[petticoat]] with a [[pink ribbon]] on her chest, another [[waist ribbon|around her waist]], and a few more [[arm ribbon|around her left arm]] (post #6420077);
* [[frills|Frilled]] white [[pajamas]] consisting of a [[sleeveless]] top and [[puffy shorts]] (post #6420088).
